{"tid":124643,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[耳塞耳鳴]有冇巴絲低頻聽覺受損？","createTime":"2017-02-17T18:24:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-19T03:53:23.000Z","uid":48633,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0240230f9c44f87425f4b85f08f207179692a6e6","tid":124643,"uid":48633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T18:24:56.000Z","msg":"最近左耳有耳塞耳鳴既問題，自己上網用YouTube 片做一個簡單既聽力測試，由20hz 聽到去20000hz。<br />\n<br />\n發現左耳愈低hz愈聽唔到，500 hz以下既 幾乎聽唔到(但右耳係聽到)，有D似被耳鳴聲取代。500hz 以上都聽到，但好似冇右耳咁清晰。<br />\n<br />\n平時出街愈嘈隻左耳就愈唔舒服，耳鳴耳塞感愈強，反而靜既環境好似舒服D (訓到教)。<br />\n<br />\n有冇巴絲有相關既經驗？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />想知可以點醫？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利伸 平時有聽開耳機(入耳式)既習慣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 懷疑關事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a8650b9d3100bfadd8c72d55c511c27376df1e8","tid":124643,"uid":6872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T18:32:38.000Z","msg":"你唔講唔覺 原來我都有呢個問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n幫推"},{"pid":"5ae8279d8c48ced37aec3c092c49e8d56fb0f165","tid":124643,"uid":48633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T18:35:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你唔講唔覺 原來我都有呢個問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n幫推</blockquote><br />\n唔講唔覺既意思係生活中冇咩影響/唔舒服? 咁咪幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ee4be7e1794fe2b05429c57785c01ce02b8da39","tid":124643,"uid":81197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T19:08:54.000Z","msg":"你以為你隻耳機播到500hz以下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91d2bdfab82f50fecaf46d1cddeef9f50d62bf89","tid":124643,"uid":48633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T01:10:36.000Z","msg":"<blockq